it's a blessing to you that God has given you children.

52:01.240 --> 52:04.000
If one woman in India doesn't get a child,

52:04.080 --> 52:06.170
she will go and weep and ask every god

52:07.020 --> 52:11.080
and every prophet and everyone that she should get a child.

52:11.200 --> 52:13.170
While in Germany it is going

52:13.240 --> 52:16.090
toward minus five percent growth now.

52:16.170 --> 52:19.050
They pay to a woman who has five children

52:19.130 --> 52:21.220
as much as the Prime Minister or even more than that,

52:22.060 --> 52:24.080
but she won't have, she' says, "I'll lose my figure."

52:24.170 --> 52:26.050
Where are you going to take these figures

52:26.110 --> 52:28.030
I don't understand.

52:28.130 --> 52:29.220
What are these figures for

52:30.050 --> 52:32.080
and who's interested in your figures?

52:33.170 --> 52:37.140
Why, why, why should we make ourselves so cheap?

52:38.000 --> 52:40.190
We are mothers and we should be proud of our motherhood.

52:41.030 --> 52:43.200
Motherhood is the highest thing a woman can achieve.

52:44.050 --> 52:45.200
I mean, I have achieved it,

52:46.060 --> 52:48.140
because I am a Mother for thousands.

52:49.000 --> 52:50.170
And I think that is the greatest thing

52:51.000 --> 52:53.140
that can happen to a woman is to be a mother.

52:53.240 --> 52:56.130
And Mother and a Guru, you can imagine My plight?

52:56.240 --> 53:00.020
It's much worse that you have to tell your children

53:00.100 --> 53:03.020
something to be done, and you love them so much

53:03.090 --> 53:04.190
that you don't want to say that,

53:05.030 --> 53:07.030
then you have to play some little sweet tricks

53:07.130 --> 53:09.060
with them to bring them round.

53:10.020 --> 53:12.110
It is such an interesting and a beautiful life

53:12.190 --> 53:14.130
to be a mother, we should be proud mothers.

53:14.200 --> 53:17.020
But I would say the men too are to be blamed,

53:17.100 --> 53:19.030
because they are not interested in mothers,

53:19.130 --> 53:21.080
they are interested in younger and younger girls

53:21.170 --> 53:23.110
- is a sign of perversion I tell you,

53:23.190 --> 53:26.140
it is a sign of a complete perversion.

53:27.100 --> 53:29.220
At the time of Mohammed Sahib there were many,

53:30.100 --> 53:33.170
many women and very few men because so many were killed,

53:34.050 --> 53:36.140
so Mohammed Sahib didn't know what to do.

53:37.020 --> 53:38.200
So He thought - they were pragmatic,

53:39.030 --> 53:40.130
as I told you yesterday that with the society

53:40.190 --> 53:42.080
one has be pragmatic - so He said, "All right,

53:42.160 --> 53:44.140
we have to have marriages," because

53:44.240 --> 53:49.080
without marriage any relationship of any kind is adharmic,

53:49.160 --> 53:52.020
is against the valencies.

53:52.110 --> 53:54.000
So He said, "We must have marriage.

53:54.060 --> 53:56.110
All right, now we have many women

53:56.190 --> 53:58.240
so let us have distribution of women

53:59.050 --> 54:00.140
according to the men we have.

54:00.240 --> 54:03.160
If you have more men then we'll have the other way around.

54:04.000 --> 54:05.020
But we have to marry,"

54:05.080 --> 54:09.000
means we have to take a collective sanction,

54:09.110 --> 54:13.020
a collective sanction has to be there, to be blessed.

54:13.120 --> 54:15.130
So He said, "All right, marry five.”

54:15.210 --> 54:18.100
But He, Himself, you see, was surprised,

54:18.150 --> 54:20.010
at time people were so sensitive,

54:20.090 --> 54:21.090
they would not marry young girls,

54:21.150 --> 54:23.010
the old men would not marry young girls.

54:23.070 --> 54:25.200
They said, "How can we marry these young girls?" you see.

54:26.020 --> 54:27.230
So He said, "No, all right, I'll marry one,

54:28.050 --> 54:29.150
because where will these young girls go,

54:29.210 --> 54:31.070
there are no young men left, so what to do?"

54:31.150 --> 54:34.150
But these days, if you ask an old man of eighty years,

54:34.230 --> 54:38.150
he would be very willing to marry a girl of eighteen years.

54:38.240 --> 54:42.230
Stupid old fool I call him, because he doesn't understand.

54:43.130 --> 54:45.240
He doesn't understand that this girl

54:46.070 --> 54:48.070
is not going to respect him as a husband

54:48.160 --> 54:50.150
and he cannot enjoy the life of a husband.

54:50.230 --> 54:53.210
He's a grandfather, or call it a great grandfather,

54:54.070 --> 54:56.040
he should behave like a great grandfather;

54:56.130 --> 54:57.230
that's an ideal relationship

54:58.090 --> 55:00.150
he should have with a young girl.

55:01.200 --> 55:04.040
All these ideals are confused today,

55:04.150 --> 55:05.230
our relationships with others.

55:06.050 --> 55:09.100
Every woman has to be attractive, why?

55:09.240 --> 55:11.160
Every man has to be attractive, why?

55:11.230 --> 55:14.120
For what? What are you going to achieve out of it?

55:15.210 --> 55:17.230
What is the utility?

55:19.090 --> 55:20.150
Attractiveness is all right

55:20.230 --> 55:24.100
as long as you are not repulsive,

55:24.210 --> 55:29.090
as long as you keep the ideal relationship with others,

55:29.210 --> 55:32.150
if the relationship becomes nothing but like a dog

55:32.240 --> 55:34.020
and bitch's one,

55:34.120 --> 55:37.100
it's better not to have this kind of an idea,

55:37.230 --> 55:41.070
it's absolutely wrong to run after something

55:41.150 --> 55:42.180
which is not our way.

55:43.020 --> 55:45.050
Human beings have to live with dignity

55:45.190 --> 55:48.140
and with complete sense of idealism

55:48.200 --> 55:50.200
as far as their relationship

55:51.010 --> 55:55.040
with each other is concerned.

55:55.170 --> 55:58.070
If you just say, "What's wrong?"

55:59.010 --> 56:01.180
then it's an argument, everything is wrong,

56:02.010 --> 56:02.230
and everything is wrong,

56:03.070 --> 56:06.090
it is not one wrong but all, everything is wrong.

56:06.210 --> 56:10.150
But if you want to have a flowering society,

56:11.030 --> 56:13.230
then you must keep to your ideals of your family life,

56:14.060 --> 56:15.120
that's a very important thing,

56:15.210 --> 56:18.030
but it happens to you as soon as you get Realization.

56:18.140 --> 56:21.210
I don't have to give a lecture on that. You just do it.

56:22.120 --> 56:24.240
You just become very nice husband

56:25.100 --> 56:28.010
and a very nice wife.

56:29.040 --> 56:32.000
Beautiful families can come out of Sahaja Yoga,

56:32.100 --> 56:34.170
there are so many, you'll see them.

56:36.010 --> 56:38.230
There are so many beautiful families now in Sahaja Yoga

56:39.070 --> 56:41.170
and now the great children,

56:42.040 --> 56:44.200
the great sages who wanted to be born

56:45.030 --> 56:46.150
are being born to them.

56:46.230 --> 56:49.090
Many great children want to be born in this England.

56:49.170 --> 56:51.100
And there are many who are born,

56:51.210 --> 56:53.060
but I don't know how they are treated,

56:53.140 --> 56:54.150
if people understand them or not.

56:54.240 --> 56:57.040
They have no vibrations to see if they are sages or not.

56:57.150 --> 57:01.090
But born realized children are so many in England,

57:02.030 --> 57:07.120
that I'm regretting sometimes the way they are treated.

57:08.140 --> 57:11.180
Nobody knows they are born realized - the way they talk,

57:12.040 --> 57:14.140
they talk nothing but wisdom.

57:15.030 --> 57:18.100
All these children are being insulted and humiliated

57:18.200 --> 57:21.180
by us who are so ignorant about them.

57:22.030 --> 57:24.010
I must say that they are very brave,

57:24.110 --> 57:26.080
they're very courageous to take birth

57:26.150 --> 57:28.150
in the countries where they are not appreciated

57:29.000 --> 57:30.060
and looked after.

57:30.200 --> 57:32.140
Another extreme is in our country,

57:32.220 --> 57:36.060
I should say, where people will sell their whole country

57:36.140 --> 57:38.030
for the sake of their children.

57:38.140 --> 57:40.190
I mean, that's going too far,

57:41.140 --> 57:43.110
that's another nonsense we do.

57:44.000 --> 57:46.200
But something in between is that you love your children,

57:47.010 --> 57:50.090
respect them; they are your trust, they are realized souls,

57:50.170 --> 57:52.060
they are sages.

57:52.140 --> 57:55.010
They are the foundations of the new world

57:55.090 --> 57:56.170
that is going to come,

57:57.010 --> 57:59.200
and this is what it is a mother has to learn.

58:00.040 --> 58:02.230
The dignity of a mother must be respected.

58:03.040 --> 58:06.030
I'm sure you all must have respected your mothers very much.

58:06.140 --> 58:10.150
But now as mothers I don't know if you will be respected.

58:13.120 --> 58:15.030
Once this is established,

58:15.140 --> 58:19.140
that a mother itself is the highest position a woman

58:19.200 --> 58:21.200
can reach and she is to be respected,

58:22.040 --> 58:24.180
all the priorities will change among women also.

58:25.040 --> 58:26.120
Because what can they do?

58:26.200 --> 58:28.060
They have no place as mothers,

58:28.130 --> 58:30.180
so they just get fed up of their children, they think,

58:31.010 --> 58:33.160
"What's the use of this motherhood? It's a thankless job."

58:35.020 --> 58:39.070
All this can only change when man changes within himself,

58:39.150 --> 58:41.060
when the transformation takes place.

58:41.150 --> 58:43.210
Just now it is just a, one of the sermons

58:44.050 --> 58:46.240
that you could hear somewhere in a very,

58:47.210 --> 58:50.040
I should say, an orthodox place.

58:50.160 --> 58:54.100
But the whole of this orthodoxy becomes part and parcel

58:54.160 --> 58:57.050
of you and you become so much tuned with it,

58:57.130 --> 58:59.140
absolutely tuned with it. You like it.

58:59.240 --> 59:03.050
You like to love your wife and nobody else in that way.

59:03.180 --> 59:08.180
And the husband likes to love her in a special way,

59:09.080 --> 59:12.190
while the wife wants to love the husband in a special way.

59:13.030 --> 59:15.060
It happens. There's no insecurity.

59:15.120 --> 59:16.230
Otherwise, you come back home and you find your wife

59:17.050 --> 59:18.090
has eloped with somebody -

59:18.170 --> 59:20.120
imagine what a situation it is.

59:20.230 --> 59:24.020
I mean, since I came and first year I got such a shock.

59:24.100 --> 59:26.170
We had a neighbor she was forty-eight years of age

59:27.000 --> 59:29.000
and her son was about twenty-two

59:29.080 --> 59:30.200
and he had a friend about twenty years.

59:31.000 --> 59:34.110
This lady eloped with that twenty-year-old boy,

59:34.210 --> 59:36.210
and she had three other children whom she left.

59:37.050 --> 59:39.210
The house was sold, the whole household,

59:40.040 --> 59:41.160
because under law she gets half,

59:41.240 --> 59:44.100
half of the property or something like that,

59:44.240 --> 59:47.000
and the three daughters are now on the streets,

59:47.080 --> 59:49.080
the younger three children were daughters are on the street,

59:49.160 --> 59:50.110
who is going to look after them?

59:50.190 --> 59:52.080
The lady, forty-eight-year-old lady,

59:52.160 --> 59:54.050
is still a bride, do you know?

59:54.130 --> 59:57.020
Going to the church and getting married.

59:58.020 --> 01:00:01.190
There's no dignity in this, no love, no affection.

01:00:03.110 --> 01:00:06.160
Christ you follow, Christ has said,

01:00:07.110 --> 01:00:11.030
"You say 'Thou shall not commit adultery,' I say,

01:00:11.130 --> 01:00:14.220
'Thou shall not have adulterous eyes.'"

01:00:15.080 --> 01:00:18.140
He's gone up to that subtle stage.

01:00:19.190 --> 01:00:23.100
We follow Christ, we wear cross, we go to the church.

01:00:23.170 --> 01:00:24.240
Where are we?

01:00:25.100 --> 01:00:29.050
So I come to another centre now, is the Vishuddhi.

01:00:29.140 --> 01:00:32.050
This is a very important centre in human beings,

01:00:32.140 --> 01:00:35.160
because when this centre is awakened

01:00:36.240 --> 01:00:39.030
you become the witness.

01:00:39.190 --> 01:00:41.050
You become the collective.

01:00:41.110 --> 01:00:44.020
This is the centre of the collective being.

01:00:44.190 --> 01:00:47.120
You become, again I say, you become the collective being,

01:00:47.200 --> 01:00:49.170
when this centre is awakened.

01:00:50.000 --> 01:00:51.160
Is a very important centre,

01:00:52.070 --> 01:00:54.210
and now as I'm with you I must tell about

01:00:55.040 --> 01:00:58.160
what we suffer from and what Indians suffer from,

01:00:59.010 --> 01:01:01.020
what the Eastern people suffer from is another thing.

01:01:01.090 --> 01:01:04.070
For example, Eastern people suffer from too much talking

01:01:04.150 --> 01:01:06.050
- right side Vishuddhi we call it -

01:01:06.130 --> 01:01:08.210
and the western suffer from not talking at all;

01:01:09.040 --> 01:01:11.040
specially English, they never talk.

01:01:13.010 --> 01:01:15.190
Actually you have to pinch them!

01:01:17.120 --> 01:01:19.200
And they never laugh, that's the problem is, they

01:01:20.030 --> 01:01:22.170
just smile and is regarded good manners,

01:01:23.000 --> 01:01:25.120
but this bit sometimes very boring.

01:01:26.220 --> 01:01:29.030
Now the Left Vishuddhi is a thing

01:01:29.120 --> 01:01:33.010
which is very much, much more subtler than what we think of,

01:01:33.110 --> 01:01:36.190
is a very funny sort of a situation

01:01:37.050 --> 01:01:38.140
where you get a Left Vishuddhi

01:01:39.000 --> 01:01:42.150
and that you get very commonly among the western people,

01:01:43.010 --> 01:01:47.010
because they have developed a new sense of guilt.

01:01:48.190 --> 01:01:50.090
I mean everybody is guilty.

01:01:50.190 --> 01:01:53.030
Without going to the courts, without committing any guilt,

01:01:53.090 --> 01:01:56.000
everybody is guilty all the time.

01:01:56.110 --> 01:01:59.090
Like a lady, "Oh, I'm so guilty."

01:01:59.170 --> 01:02:00.150
"What happened?"

01:02:00.220 --> 01:02:02.050
"I didn't say 'thank you' to her."

01:02:02.120 --> 01:02:05.060
So it doesn't matter. What is there to be guilty after all?

01:02:05.200 --> 01:02:07.050
"Oh I'm so guilty."

01:02:07.120 --> 01:02:08.080
"What happened?"

01:02:08.150 --> 01:02:11.110
"I spilt some coffee." So all right, doesn't matter,

01:02:11.190 --> 01:02:13.190
it can be cleared out, what is there to be guilty?

01:02:14.040 --> 01:02:17.040
But it is an unknown guilt people have,

01:02:17.120 --> 01:02:18.200
they don't know why they are guilty,

01:02:19.040 --> 01:02:21.070
why they are getting all the time this feeling.

01:02:21.140 --> 01:02:22.240
"Oh God, I should not have done it,

01:02:23.040 --> 01:02:26.040
I should not have done that." What guilt?

01:02:27.000 --> 01:02:29.020
What guilt we can have?

01:02:29.130 --> 01:02:33.000
And this guilt is a horrifying thing.

01:02:33.160 --> 01:02:37.190
I have seen - start from America,

01:02:38.020 --> 01:02:41.160
England, Portugal, Spain,

01:02:42.060 --> 01:02:44.200
Italy, all that, Switzerland,

01:02:45.050 --> 01:02:48.060
all these places nothing - but Left Vishuddhi

01:02:48.160 --> 01:02:52.030
is the first problem and the last which I have to conquer.

01:02:52.140 --> 01:02:53.220
One lady got up and she said,

01:02:54.050 --> 01:02:56.080
"Mother I am guilty because of Vietnam."

01:02:56.160 --> 01:02:59.020
I said, "Vietnam? It is finished long time back now,

01:02:59.090 --> 01:03:00.160
what are you going to do about it?"

01:03:00.210 --> 01:03:03.070
No, but I'm guilty about it." "But why?

01:03:03.130 --> 01:03:06.060
What are you going to do about it, how are you concerned with it,

01:03:06.180 --> 01:03:09.240
what is your relationship with it, why are you guilty?"

01:03:10.070 --> 01:03:11.130
"I just feel guilty."

01:03:11.210 --> 01:03:13.230
I said, "It's nonsense."

01:03:14.130 --> 01:03:16.240
Like that everybody has developed this thing.

01:03:17.040 --> 01:03:18.180
Now from where does it come?

01:03:19.030 --> 01:03:23.210
Let's see the source. The first source comes from Bible,

01:03:24.070 --> 01:03:26.240
which is very wrongly interpreted, saying that,

01:03:27.070 --> 01:03:28.180
"You are a sinner, a born sinner."

01:03:29.000 --> 01:03:33.060
I mean its absurd. What it means is that,

01:03:33.180 --> 01:03:36.120
that you are the one who is only aware of the sins,

01:03:36.180 --> 01:03:38.070
not the animals.

01:03:38.150 --> 01:03:41.180
You are the one who is aware of your ignorance,

01:03:42.010 --> 01:03:43.060
not the animals.

01:03:43.140 --> 01:03:46.000
You are the one who is aware of your blindness,

01:03:46.070 --> 01:03:47.240
others are not, animals are not.

01:03:48.070 --> 01:03:50.060
Why?

01:03:50.140 --> 01:03:55.070
Because within you is developed that I-ness,

01:03:55.180 --> 01:03:57.120
that I-ness as I told you yesterday

01:03:57.200 --> 01:04:01.060
is developed because of the ego and the super ego meeting here.

01:04:01.140 --> 01:04:03.000
Because you raised your head,

01:04:03.070 --> 01:04:06.010
because this chakra was to be enlightened.

01:04:06.090 --> 01:04:11.170
You raised your head and this ego and super ego

01:04:11.230 --> 01:04:14.030
went and met here, it calcified,

01:04:14.090 --> 01:04:17.010
you got your I-ness and that's why you think,

01:04:17.070 --> 01:04:19.000
"I've done wrong or I've done right."

01:04:19.090 --> 01:04:21.180
Animals don't think like that, they are not bothered.

01:04:22.060 --> 01:04:24.090
They have to do what they do, they want to do that.

01:04:24.170 --> 01:04:26.170
they never sit down and say, "I am guilty."

01:04:27.030 --> 01:04:29.230
Have you ever met any animal who says that? -

01:04:30.240 --> 01:04:33.140
except for the human beings, all the time.

01:04:33.230 --> 01:04:36.000
Now this has come to, it's a myth,

01:04:36.080 --> 01:04:38.140
it is a very big myth with which you are living.

01:04:38.230 --> 01:04:41.220
It’s absolutely myth, believe Me;

01:04:42.200 --> 01:04:45.030
there is nothing like guilt.

01:04:45.140 --> 01:04:48.140
And this guilt is eating you off all the time,

01:04:48.220 --> 01:04:50.050
it's making you an inertia,

01:04:50.140 --> 01:04:53.220
it is making you feel so much lost,

01:04:54.070 --> 01:04:57.150
and this centre is very important

01:04:58.180 --> 01:05:00.020
to be opened out.

01:05:00.090 --> 01:05:03.100
So first of all before I start any program, I tell them

01:05:03.180 --> 01:05:05.190
one mantra you should say, "Mother I am not guilty,

01:05:06.020 --> 01:05:08.210
Mother I am not guilty," sixteen times,

01:05:09.040 --> 01:05:11.010
that's the punishment for being guilty.

01:05:11.070 --> 01:05:12.230
If you are guilty you must go into punishment, all right?

01:05:13.050 --> 01:05:14.120
So this is the punishment for you,

01:05:14.180 --> 01:05:17.020
is to say, "Mother I am not guilty, Mother I am not guilty."

01:05:17.100 --> 01:05:20.020
Say it sixteen times, and that's how you get rid of it.

01:05:20.120 --> 01:05:22.240
It's so practical, it works out.

01:05:23.070 --> 01:05:26.050
With that you get spondylitis, you get pain in the heart,

01:05:26.130 --> 01:05:28.230
you get this hand what you call frigid hand,

01:05:29.050 --> 01:05:31.090
all problems you get with that,

01:05:31.160 --> 01:05:34.110
and that is all because of this mythical guilt

01:05:34.190 --> 01:05:35.190
you are working out.

01:05:36.020 --> 01:05:37.170
Now the another myth comes,

01:05:38.000 --> 01:05:40.240
the source of it I think is the psychologist,

01:05:41.100 --> 01:05:42.220
the so-called psychologist.

01:05:43.050 --> 01:05:44.210
They have no sense of psyche,

01:05:45.050 --> 01:05:47.060
because they have no way of entering into psyche,

01:05:47.160 --> 01:05:50.080
what they are doing is recording, finding out,

01:05:50.160 --> 01:05:51.210
and trying to cure people.

01:05:52.030 --> 01:05:54.100
How many mad people have they cured?

01:05:55.020 --> 01:05:57.060
Sahaja Yoga must have cured hundreds.

01:05:57.140 --> 01:05:59.130
How many mad people have they cured?

01:05:59.220 --> 01:06:00.240
They have not cured anyone.

01:06:01.070 --> 01:06:03.050
On the contrary, if you go to a psychologist,

01:06:03.140 --> 01:06:07.030
you might become more mad, the way they are mad themselves;

01:06:07.130 --> 01:06:12.030
because these psychologists, when they talk to people,

01:06:12.130 --> 01:06:15.050
they don't know they are dealing with pathological cases,

01:06:15.140 --> 01:06:17.020
abnormal cases.

01:06:17.100 --> 01:06:19.100
And when you deal with the pathological cases,

01:06:19.170 --> 01:06:23.050
you yourself get intoxicated by that,

01:06:23.130 --> 01:06:26.140
or you can say that there is contamination.

01:06:26.240 --> 01:06:28.160
And you don't know how to protect yourself.

01:06:28.240 --> 01:06:31.220
Jung is the only psychologist, I would say,

01:06:32.040 --> 01:06:33.240
because he was quite a prophet/perfect person,

01:06:34.050 --> 01:06:36.020
after he got realization, who talked of it,

01:06:36.100 --> 01:06:39.020
that a physician can get sick.

