Switzerland, Geneva, so much better, what's happening?

01:22:11.130 --> 01:22:16.090
Here they run after a man who is asking for a Rolls Royce,

01:22:17.080 --> 01:22:19.050
a fellow who asks for a 59-th Rolls Royce,

01:22:19.130 --> 01:22:21.020
they starve themselves

01:22:21.090 --> 01:22:23.170
and made a Rolls Royce for him and when he came,

01:22:24.000 --> 01:22:25.140
they gave him the Rolls Royce, imagine?

01:22:26.000 --> 01:22:27.220
They said he's a perfect master.

01:22:28.050 --> 01:22:30.080
There is no pure intelligence left in the mind

01:22:30.140 --> 01:22:32.240
to understand that how can you get Spirit

01:22:33.050 --> 01:22:35.170
for this nonsensical Rolls Royce?

01:22:36.130 --> 01:22:39.060
At least Derbyshire are not, people from Derbyshire

01:22:39.130 --> 01:22:41.190
should not be impressed by that very much,

01:22:42.050 --> 01:22:44.140
because they make it here.

01:22:45.190 --> 01:22:48.060
You cannot make God, can you?

01:22:48.200 --> 01:22:51.000
You can make Rolls Royces, all right,

01:22:51.100 --> 01:22:53.240
can you exchange Rolls Royce for God?

01:22:54.160 --> 01:22:56.130
They are running after such horrible things,

01:22:56.200 --> 01:22:58.140
like horrible another thing that somebody

01:22:58.200 --> 01:23:00.100
is trying to teach you how to fly.

01:23:00.190 --> 01:23:02.130
The wife of the director is sitting here

01:23:02.210 --> 01:23:04.200
who started is suffering with epilepsy -

01:23:05.020 --> 01:23:07.030
her husband got epilepsy, her daughter got epilepsy,

01:23:07.130 --> 01:23:08.170
they all were epileptic,

01:23:09.000 --> 01:23:10.240
and they were paying thousands of pounds,

01:23:11.050 --> 01:23:13.080
three thousand pounds to fly,

01:23:13.160 --> 01:23:18.130
and they starting hopping themselves like a frog. Imagine!

01:23:19.170 --> 01:23:21.130
With pure intelligence you must ask

01:23:21.220 --> 01:23:25.200
that guru to drop himself from the leaning Tower of Pisa,

01:23:26.030 --> 01:23:27.190
I think it was made only for that,

01:23:28.050 --> 01:23:32.240
and see if he can fly even one inch higher.

01:23:33.210 --> 01:23:35.170
Why not use your intelligence?

01:23:35.230 --> 01:23:37.180
You are supposed to be most balanced

01:23:38.010 --> 01:23:40.010
and intelligent people.

01:23:41.070 --> 01:23:44.000
Yesterday I told you that you are placed,

01:23:44.110 --> 01:23:48.160
the most important place in the Universe is the Heart,

01:23:49.000 --> 01:23:51.070
England is the Heart of the Universe

01:23:51.170 --> 01:23:54.220
and the Heart is lethargic.

01:23:56.030 --> 01:23:57.050
What can I do?

01:23:57.130 --> 01:23:59.130
You have to tell Me, what am I to do,

01:23:59.210 --> 01:24:02.180
to pump this Heart into reality.

01:24:03.020 --> 01:24:05.020
There are seekers, I would not say there are seekers,

01:24:05.080 --> 01:24:08.240
When it came to hippieism, thousands became hippies.

01:24:09.140 --> 01:24:11.210
But all absurd things they accept very easily

01:24:12.030 --> 01:24:15.110
and why not the thing that you are seeking?

01:24:16.020 --> 01:24:18.160
It's beyond My mind. I cannot understand.

01:24:18.240 --> 01:24:21.020
Now I didn't come to this place as an immigrant, as I told

01:24:21.080 --> 01:24:25.050
you. I was, just came, I came here because something happened

01:24:25.130 --> 01:24:27.140
and My husband got elected to this country,

01:24:27.240 --> 01:24:29.190
which was important, which was,

01:24:30.030 --> 01:24:32.240
I think, was pre-ordained. It was to be.

01:24:33.130 --> 01:24:37.220
But I have to implore you now to take to this and understand

01:24:38.160 --> 01:24:40.160
that this is what William Blake has told you

01:24:40.220 --> 01:24:46.190
that "The prophets are going to be in this country,

01:24:47.080 --> 01:24:49.200
that the God of men are going to become prophets

01:24:50.020 --> 01:24:51.170
and they are going to have the power

01:24:51.240 --> 01:24:54.000
to make others prophets." That is Sahaja Yoga.

01:24:54.110 --> 01:24:56.240
There's nothing else but this.

01:24:58.150 --> 01:25:00.000
He has promised so many things.

01:25:00.080 --> 01:25:03.050
He has even described the house where I live,

01:25:03.140 --> 01:25:06.000
he has described the house that we are occupying now,

01:25:06.080 --> 01:25:07.170
exact position.

01:25:07.230 --> 01:25:11.230
He has described the ashram where we'll lay our foundations,

01:25:12.230 --> 01:25:18.120
into such details that I'm amazed such a great sage

01:25:18.200 --> 01:25:20.140
and a seer was born in this great country

01:25:20.220 --> 01:25:24.060
and nobody wants to see it through. Now what am I to do?

01:25:26.020 --> 01:25:31.110
I hope very soon people would realize

01:25:32.090 --> 01:25:35.200
that they have to take a very big role,

01:25:36.090 --> 01:25:39.110
a very important and vital role

01:25:39.220 --> 01:25:42.060
in the transformation of the whole humanity

01:25:42.160 --> 01:25:46.060
and saving of this disastrous time.

01:25:46.220 --> 01:25:48.230
They are the ones who have to lead people

01:25:49.060 --> 01:25:51.090
into the Kingdom of God.

01:25:51.220 --> 01:25:54.020
I can hope and bless that.

01:25:54.110 --> 01:25:57.170
May God bless you!

01:26:03.220 --> 01:26:07.180
Luckily we have a very good standard

01:26:08.110 --> 01:26:10.150
of the Sahaja Yogis in Derbyshire,

01:26:11.010 --> 01:26:12.180
really it's surprising

01:26:13.040 --> 01:26:16.240
and Blake has mentioned Derbyshire very much,

01:26:17.120 --> 01:26:19.010
they wanted Me to come to Derbyshire.

01:26:19.080 --> 01:26:21.050
I said, "Birmingham has been sufficient for Me

01:26:21.110 --> 01:26:22.120
and I am not going to Derbyshire."

01:26:22.190 --> 01:26:24.010
And they said, "Mother, please." And then he said,

01:26:24.090 --> 01:26:26.080
"Blake has mentioned You come to Derbyshire."

01:26:26.160 --> 01:26:27.200
And that's how I am here

01:26:28.040 --> 01:26:32.090
and I hope that this centre will definitely create

01:26:32.180 --> 01:26:34.120
very good Sahaja Yogis.

01:26:34.230 --> 01:26:38.230
Great prophets can be created out of this,

01:26:39.060 --> 01:26:42.100
after all Blake has mentioned Derbyshire very strongly,

01:26:42.200 --> 01:26:43.170
he recommended it.

01:26:43.230 --> 01:26:46.060
But what I find today when I went for a drive,

01:26:46.150 --> 01:26:48.100
there's a lot of black magic on.

01:26:48.200 --> 01:26:52.210
People are indulging into horrible, horrible things.

01:26:53.090 --> 01:26:56.150
I was worried, quite worried.

01:26:57.040 --> 01:26:59.030
It's a very dangerous thing.

01:26:59.210 --> 01:27:01.230
It's dangerous for you, for your children,

01:27:02.040 --> 01:27:04.120
for your families, for everyone,

01:27:04.210 --> 01:27:06.170
and I found those pockets,

01:27:07.030 --> 01:27:09.210
I was amazed how they are prospering here.

01:27:10.070 --> 01:27:15.140
May God give you strength and proper wisdom

01:27:15.230 --> 01:27:20.000
to understand how you are placed in relation

01:27:20.170 --> 01:27:23.100
to the great work of God.

01:27:30.210 --> 01:27:32.040
Now if you have any questions,

01:27:32.100 --> 01:27:33.120
we can have for about for five minutes,

01:27:33.200 --> 01:27:35.060
yesterday many people asked many questions,

01:27:35.120 --> 01:27:38.040
actually first day only I allow people to ask questions

01:27:38.150 --> 01:27:40.090
because second day it is quite a waste of time.

01:27:40.150 --> 01:27:42.230
Now don't ask personal questions for heaven's sake,

01:27:43.070 --> 01:27:44.210
don't ask any personal question.

01:27:45.030 --> 01:27:47.170
That we'll attend to them later on, personally,

01:27:48.010 --> 01:27:49.040
they can be attended to;

01:27:49.120 --> 01:27:50.240
but anything general if you want to ask,

01:27:51.060 --> 01:27:53.210
please ask the question general.

01:28:07.030 --> 01:28:08.200
Audience question: Have You seen God Yourself?

01:28:09.020 --> 01:28:10.060
Why do you ask this question?

01:28:10.120 --> 01:28:12.110
Are you authorized to ask that question?

01:28:13.060 --> 01:28:15.200
First you see your Spirit and then we'll talk about it.

01:28:16.050 --> 01:28:17.110
Why should you ask such a question?

01:28:17.170 --> 01:28:20.230
Are you an Indian? Then at least keep some manners.

01:28:21.060 --> 01:28:22.110
Please be seated.

01:28:22.220 --> 01:28:24.230
This kind of an arrogant question should not be asked,

01:28:25.060 --> 01:28:27.030
"Have You seen God?"

01:28:27.160 --> 01:28:28.230
Why should you ask Me such a question?

01:28:29.050 --> 01:28:31.170
What authority have you got to ask that question to Me?

01:28:32.030 --> 01:28:34.110
I have to ask you question: have you felt your Spirit?

01:28:34.190 --> 01:28:36.050
All right, first feel your Spirit,

01:28:36.120 --> 01:28:38.110
that's why Buddha never talked of God,

01:28:38.190 --> 01:28:39.220
I yesterday only told you;

01:28:40.060 --> 01:28:42.020
because suddenly you want to see God -

01:28:42.090 --> 01:28:43.120
have you got eyes to see God?

01:28:43.200 --> 01:28:46.110
You can't see Me even, how can you see God?

01:28:50.190 --> 01:28:54.000
First of all become your Spirit, then we'll talk about it.

01:28:54.060 --> 01:28:56.020
A little child won't go

01:28:56.090 --> 01:29:01.080
and talk to a king and slap him on the face, will he?

01:29:01.230 --> 01:29:03.220
Is he supposed to do that?

01:29:04.090 --> 01:29:06.200
We must know our boundaries, our maryadas.

01:29:07.080 --> 01:29:10.200
Specially Indians must know, I'm surprised sometimes.

01:29:11.130 --> 01:29:12.200
To ask such a question like that:

01:29:13.030 --> 01:29:15.020
"Have you seen God?" Whether I've seen Him or not,

01:29:15.080 --> 01:29:17.080
why should I tell you? But what does he say?...

01:29:22.070 --> 01:29:25.170
Doesn't behoove, doesn't behoove you. It is very arrogant.

01:29:25.240 --> 01:29:28.070
I am surprised that you've learned such ways here,

01:29:28.130 --> 01:29:32.230
it is never done by an Indian, it's very embarrassing.

01:29:34.180 --> 01:29:36.090
Just imagine, if I have seen it,

01:29:36.170 --> 01:29:38.020
is he going to believe Me? -

01:29:38.150 --> 01:29:41.010
or not seen it (Hindi).

01:29:47.180 --> 01:29:52.180
...All this come and come somethimes I feel.

01:29:56.190 --> 01:30:00.100
I mean, what a question it is, “Have You seen or not?”

01:30:21.190 --> 01:30:25.070
But he's a Master of Philosophy from Benares University,

01:30:25.130 --> 01:30:27.170
and all that, but in India you won't find such people,

01:30:27.230 --> 01:30:30.030
I don't know from where these materialistic,

01:30:30.110 --> 01:30:32.090
absolutely gross people are,

01:30:32.170 --> 01:30:34.160
I mean what a question to ask Me?

01:30:39.200 --> 01:30:42.030
It's never done.

01:30:46.240 --> 01:30:50.190
I'm here to give you Self Realization, that's all.

01:30:51.080 --> 01:30:55.080
And you should get it, that's your right.

01:30:56.050 --> 01:30:57.230
This is a bank I should say

01:30:58.060 --> 01:31:00.230
and I have to sign your checks, that's all.

01:31:01.200 --> 01:31:05.220
If you get your checks signed, that's all,

01:31:06.050 --> 01:31:07.190
finished, that's My relationship with you,

01:31:08.020 --> 01:31:09.140
I'm not going to tell you about Myself

01:31:09.220 --> 01:31:11.110
to get crucified again.

01:31:13.140 --> 01:31:15.110
Christ tried to tell something about Himself,

01:31:16.000 --> 01:31:17.190
and they crucified Him.

01:31:18.060 --> 01:31:21.170
Now if I tell him, "Of course I know about God,"

01:31:22.030 --> 01:31:23.060
he is not going to accept.

01:31:23.160 --> 01:31:26.190
If I say, "I don't know," then he is not going to accept.

01:31:27.040 --> 01:31:28.100
Stupid.

01:31:28.160 --> 01:31:30.210
Indians are not stupid at all, they are very wise people,

01:31:31.040 --> 01:31:31.210
I must say.

01:31:32.040 --> 01:31:35.130
I am surprised from where this stupidity has come.

01:31:38.040 --> 01:31:39.070
Very wise.

01:31:39.130 --> 01:31:41.150
Indians are very wise because it’s a yoga bhoomi, you know,

01:31:41.210 --> 01:31:44.110
such a, it’s such an ancient country of ours.

01:31:44.190 --> 01:31:47.150
You don't know the praises of this country I can ...

01:31:48.120 --> 01:31:51.150
Do not judge them by the people you see, no, no, no, no, no.

01:31:52.000 --> 01:31:56.000
It’s very great country, it’s very great, it’s spiritual,

01:31:56.060 --> 01:31:57.220
absolute spiritual country.

01:31:58.060 --> 01:32:00.140
See these are I don't know what's the matter with them,

01:32:00.220 --> 01:32:02.030
very superficial people have come here,

01:32:02.110 --> 01:32:03.180
extremely superficial.

01:32:04.010 --> 01:32:06.030
There are some great souls also I say,

01:32:06.120 --> 01:32:10.220
but don't judge, don't judge that great country.

01:32:11.090 --> 01:32:14.120
Once I was going to India with My husband and I told him,

01:32:14.200 --> 01:32:16.090
"We've touched our country." And he said, "How do You know?"

01:32:16.170 --> 01:32:18.120
I said, "See, the vibrations!

01:32:18.210 --> 01:32:23.010
The whole country is vibrating, the atmosphere is vibrating."

01:32:23.200 --> 01:32:24.170
He said, "Really?"

01:32:25.000 --> 01:32:26.120
I said, "You go and ask the pilot."

01:32:26.210 --> 01:32:28.240
We were in the first class, he went down and he asked him.

01:32:29.090 --> 01:32:32.030
He said, "Sir, we just touched it about a minute back."

01:32:33.000 --> 01:32:35.140
Such a great country like that,

01:32:36.010 --> 01:32:38.020
the whole, the Kundalini of the Universe

01:32:38.100 --> 01:32:40.010
resides in that country, can you imagine -

01:32:40.100 --> 01:32:44.050
the Kundalini. And they have no desire to seek,

01:32:44.130 --> 01:32:46.120
that's the power of desire that resides there,

01:32:46.210 --> 01:32:48.040
and they have no power to seek.

01:32:48.120 --> 01:32:50.190
Can you imagine? (Hindi)

01:32:51.210 --> 01:32:53.130
I am Myself surprised

01:32:53.240 --> 01:32:55.200
and those who have come also like gurus,

01:32:56.070 --> 01:32:58.150
horrible people making money,

01:32:59.150 --> 01:33:03.070
I'm ashamed if I am an Indian by any chance or if,

01:33:03.180 --> 01:33:07.010
as I'm ashamed I sometimes feel,

01:33:07.240 --> 01:33:09.240
"What have they done to what we had?"

01:33:10.070 --> 01:33:13.240
They have such a tremendous heritage, you are just a shoot,

01:33:14.080 --> 01:33:17.150
you are just the outside, you are the tree,

01:33:17.240 --> 01:33:20.160
we are the roots, you can't live without us,

01:33:21.010 --> 01:33:25.180
we are your roots and these roots I see I can't understand.

01:33:34.040 --> 01:33:39.020
Still it's all right, it's the concern of a Mother.

01:33:40.030 --> 01:33:42.060
Let's have it. Now, put your hands towards Me, please.

01:33:42.160 --> 01:33:45.030
All of you take out your shoes. You must have seeking.

01:33:45.110 --> 01:33:46.060
If you have no seeking,

01:33:46.170 --> 01:33:48.220
what's the use of coming to My program?
